    "Our primary interest lies in determining the efficiency with which informationâ€\"or rather disinformationâ€\"propagates within these disinformation networks.",
    "With this goal in mind, we will contrast disinformation actors against journalists as legitimate sources of information.",
    "Unlike anonymous users or those with obscured identities who might engage in the propagation of disinformation, journalists are publicly identifiable entities, which imparts a certain degree of accountability and transparency to their actions on these platforms (Molyneux et al. 2020).",
    "They are tethered to the media outlets they represent, which typically uphold strict editorial standards and scrutiny before releasing content (Nielsen et al. 2020).",
